  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Childcare Teacher",
  "description": "<ul><li>Position Title:<strong> Preschool English & Chinese Teacher</strong></li><li>Working Location: North-East</li><li>Duration: Full-Time</li><li>Low Staff Child Ratio</li></ul><p><strong>Job Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Plan, develop, and implement age-appropriate class activities for children.</li><li>Prepare and implement the programs and age-appropriate teaching aids.</li><li>Set up and create a stimulating, engaging, and pleasant learning environment that promotes self-directed learning and holistic development.</li><li>Use positive discipline techniques at all times.</li><li>Maintain good communication and partnerships with parents, providing regular updates on their child's progress.</li><li>Collaborate with fellow teachers and staff to ensure a cohesive and supportive learning environment.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least a Diploma in Early Childhood Education – Teaching (DECCE-T) or a Degree in Early Childhood Care</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>A genuine passion for nurturing and educating young children</li></ul><p>If you believe you have what it takes to join our team of dedicated and passionate preschool teachers, please submit your resume, cover letter, and any relevant certifications via whatsapp @ mobile 85080588. We look forward to hearing from you!</p>",
